                     <interp inst="t18481127-172-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>, stealing 2 blankets 1 apron, and 6 razors value 33<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18481127-name-883" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18481127-name-883" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
